<subSubSection id="C34B6535FF83FFBB055A4312FB0672B2" pageId="36" pageNumber="542" type="description">
<paragraph id="8BEE36BEFF83FFBB055A4312FB4573EF" blockId="36.[826,1441,1031,1176]" pageId="36" pageNumber="542">
Previously 
<emphasis id="B925EAACFF83FFBB05DF4312FA827343" box="[959,1378,1062,1083]" italics="true" pageId="36" pageNumber="542">
<taxonomicName id="4C514D3DFF83FFBB05DF4312FABE7343" baseAuthorityName="P. L. Sclater" baseAuthorityYear="1866" box="[959,1374,1062,1083]" class="Aves" family="Caprimulgidae" genus="Caprimulgus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Caprimulgiformes" pageId="36" pageNumber="542" phylum="Chordata" rank="subSpecies" species="longirostris" subSpecies="ruficervix">Caprimulgus longirostris ruficervix</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
It is elevated to full species status. It is the sister species of 
<taxonomicName id="4C514D3DFF83FFBB05374350FC007301" baseAuthorityName="Chapman" baseAuthorityYear="1929" box="[855,992,1124,1145]" class="Aves" family="Caprimulgidae" genus="Hydropsalis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Caprimulgiformes" pageId="36" pageNumber="542" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="roraimae">
<emphasis id="B925EAACFF83FFBB05374350FC007301" box="[855,992,1124,1145]" italics="true" pageId="36" pageNumber="542">H. roraimae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Together the two species form a clade that is sister to 
<taxonomicName id="4C514D3DFF83FFBB059A43B6FB7E73EF" authorityName="Bonaparte" authorityYear="1825" box="[1018,1182,1154,1175]" class="Aves" family="Caprimulgidae" genus="Caprimulgus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Caprimulgiformes" pageId="36" pageNumber="542" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="longirostris">
<emphasis id="B925EAACFF83FFBB059A43B6FB7E73EF" box="[1018,1182,1154,1175]" italics="true" pageId="36" pageNumber="542">H. longirostris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BEE36BEFF83FFBB055A43FBFC4A739C" blockId="36.[826,1441,1231,1375]" box="[826,938,1231,1252]" pageId="36" pageNumber="542">
<emphasis id="B925EAACFF83FFBB055A43FBFC4A739C" box="[826,938,1231,1252]" italics="true" pageId="36" pageNumber="542">Diagnosis</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BEE36BEFF83FFBB055A43D9FAA17227" blockId="36.[826,1441,1231,1375]" pageId="36" pageNumber="542">
Intermediate in size and body shape to 
<taxonomicName id="4C514D3DFF83FFBB029D43DAFA41727A" authorityName="Bonaparte" authorityYear="1825" box="[1277,1441,1261,1283]" class="Aves" family="Caprimulgidae" genus="Caprimulgus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Caprimulgiformes" pageId="36" pageNumber="542" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="longirostris">
<emphasis id="B925EAACFF83FFBB029D43DAFA41727A" box="[1277,1441,1261,1283]" italics="true" pageId="36" pageNumber="542">H. longirostris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="4C514D3DFF83FFBB05164239FBE0725A" baseAuthorityName="Chapman" baseAuthorityYear="1929" box="[886,1024,1293,1314]" class="Aves" family="Caprimulgidae" genus="Hydropsalis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Caprimulgiformes" pageId="36" pageNumber="542" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="roraimae">
<emphasis id="B925EAACFF83FFBB05164239FBE0725A" box="[886,1024,1293,1314]" italics="true" pageId="36" pageNumber="542">H. roraimae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Its plumage is most similar to 
<taxonomicName id="4C514D3DFF83FFBB055A421FFC237238" baseAuthorityName="Chapman" baseAuthorityYear="1929" box="[826,963,1323,1344]" class="Aves" family="Caprimulgidae" genus="Hydropsalis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Caprimulgiformes" pageId="36" pageNumber="542" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="roraimae">
<emphasis id="B925EAACFF83FFBB055A421FFC237238" box="[826,963,1323,1344]" italics="true" pageId="36" pageNumber="542">H. roraimae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, but is slightly lighter and is more distinctly cinnamon coloured, with white spots.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BEE36BEFF83FFBB055A42A2FC5172D3" blockId="36.[826,1254,1430,1483]" box="[826,945,1430,1451]" pageId="36" pageNumber="542">
<emphasis id="B925EAACFF83FFBB055A42A2FC5172D3" box="[826,945,1430,1451]" italics="true" pageId="36" pageNumber="542">Comments</emphasis>
</paragraph>
